entries.8aa4fe3f0590: This is a demo application showcasing the Lingo.dev compiler for automatic translations in React applications.
entries.999a96fc5866: Automatic extraction of translatable text from JSX
entries.b285bf7876d3: Build-time transformation with zero runtime overhead
entries.ab0450919701: Support for multiple bundlers (Vite, Webpack, Next.js)
entries.2d626508fb8f: Hash-based translation system for stable identifiers
entries.0add30e37450: The compiler analyzes your React components at build time and automatically extracts all translatable strings. It then generates translations using your configured translation provider.
entries.07d84d34dd3a: Simply add the "use i18n" directive at the top of your component files, and the compiler handles the rest!
